	(descr "DUAL-SOURCE 3.0x3.0mm shielded SMD power inductor land pattern. Accepts BOTH: CENKER CKCS3015 (LCSC C354563, 2.2uH, Isat 1.6A, DCR 60mohm, 1.7mm H) -- PREFERRED -- and Sunlord SWPA3012 (LCSC C36402, 2.2uH, Isat 1.2A, DCR 98mohm, 1.2mm H) -- drop-in alternate. Both share a 2.7mm outer pad span; pads here span the union of the two terminal patterns (x 0.35-1.35, y +/-0.75), so either part solders without a board change. Height clearance: assume 1.7mm (the taller CENKER).")
